high_descs: Turn around and begin walking to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the end of the kitchen island.
Pick up the closest metal butter knife off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and begin walking to the door, then hang a right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Use the butter knife to slice up the potato that is to the left of the kitchen sink on the counter.
Turn left and take a step, then turn right and take a step, then turn right again to face the sink.
Place the butter knife into the sink basin to the left of the tomato.
Turn right and take a step,, then turn left and take a step, then turn left again to face the sliced potato.
Pick up a piece of sliced potato off of the counter.
Walk back over to face the sink basin.
Place the piece of sliced potato into the sink basin and turn the water on, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the piece of sliced potato.
Turn right and begin walking forward, then turn right again and walk over to the microwave in the corner of the room.
Open the microwave and place the piece of clean sliced potato in the microwave then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean piece of sliced potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees, then turn left 90 degrees, then left another 90 degrees to face the counter.
Pick up the knife closer to the edge of the counter
Turn left 90 degrees, then right 90 degrees, and cross the room to the sink, turning left 90 degrees when you reach it.
Cut the potato that is in the sink.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink
Walk over to the potato slices next to the sink.
Pick up the end of the potato.
Wash the potato slice in the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the potato slice inside, close it, cook the potato, open the door when it is done cooking.
anns.task_desc: Grab a knife to slice in order to cook a potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the island in the middle of the room.
Pick up the knife closest to the edge of the counter top.
Turn to the left and walk to the sink.
Slice the potato that is beside the hand soap on the counter.
Move over to the sink basin.
Place the knife in the sink basin.
Turn right and walk closer to the sink basin.
Pick up a potato slice from the counter.
Walk back to the sink basin to the right.
Place the potato slice in the basin and wash it.
Remove the potato slice from the basin, turn right and walk to the microwave across the room.
Place the potato slice into the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Placing a potato slice in the microwave.
